      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "直到现在我才明白她为什么会做这种事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_hou_xing",
      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为……因为……",
