      "speaker_name": "夏侯星",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只要我再围着你脖子转三次，你的头颅就要落下来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
